过 5,000 万的学生提供基于华为云的中小学教育云平台服务，助力远程教育。 消费者业务不断坚持「 1+8+N 」全场景智慧生活战略，以 HarmonyOS 和 HMS 生态为核心驱动及服务能力，围绕以智慧办公、运动健康、智能家居、智慧出行和影音娱乐为主的五大生活场景，为消费者打造全场景智慧生活体验。 华为轮值董事长胡厚崑表示：「这一年，我们不畏艰难，依然坚持以创新的 ICT 技术持续为客户创造价值，助力全球科技抗疫、经济发展和社会进步，改善经营质量，全年经营业绩基本达到预期。我们将继续与客户及伙伴开放合作，推动社会、经济与环境的可持续发展。」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-599ea7f049243b876a2a69e7a628f02d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "294 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/452212619"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I78f+7NCQh7sqEAMaCDYyNzcxMDUxINq/kIMGMAI4xwNAFHIJNDUyMjEyNjE5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1617261165.4000957", "card_id": "Q_451584283", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《哥斯拉大战金刚》中金刚最后丢掉战斧，是认输还是和解？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a2bf19622aed9ebb1ca0e198bce284ae_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "273 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/451584283"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I78f+7NCQh7sqEAMaCDYyNjMxMzU1IN/w/IIGMAE4PkAVcgk0NTE1ODQyODN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1617261165.4003978", "card_id": "Q_449668091", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价拜登承诺投资 2 万亿升级美国基础设施建设？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "拜登承诺在 10 年内投资 2 万亿美元，改善美国的基建设施、扩大网络宽带、促进清洁能源发展，拜登这个计划能行吗？为什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-c249cbdac6923d3118aa81a68ee4ef3d_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "262 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/449668091"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I78f+7NCQh7sqEAMaCDYyMjA1NDczIPn1wYIGMAE4kgFAFnIJNDQ5NjY4MDkxeACqAQlia